<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
      <title>Tate Node Visualiser</title>

      <!-- build:js js/tateExpressViz.min.js -->
      <script type="text/javascript" src="js/jquery-1.11.2.min.js"></script>
      <script type="text/javascript" src="js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
      <script type="text/javascript" src="js/bootstrap3-typeahead.min.js"></script>
      <script type="text/javascript" src="js/MapManager.js"></script>
      <script type="text/javascript" src="js/mergeViews.js"></script>
      <!-- endbuild -->

      <!-- build:css css/tatestyles.min.css-->
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap.min.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap-theme.min.css">
      <link rel='stylesheet' href="css/tateExpressStyles.css">
      <!-- endbuild -->

  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="indent">
        <h1>Tate Cartography Visualisation</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="indent">
        <h2>Merge Views</h2>
    </div>

    <div id="intro">
        <div class="indent">
            <p>
                You can merge a number of maps into a new or existing one.<br><br>
                If you'd like to create a new map then simply fill in the details below. The description is optional.<br>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="indent">
            <form class="form-horizontal" ref='uploadForm' id="uploadForm" method="post" action="/processCreateGraph" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="mapName" class="col-md-1 control-label">Map Name</label>
                    <div class="col-md-5">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="mapName" id="mapName">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="mapDescription" class="col-md-1 control-label">Description</label>
                    <div class="col-md-5">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="mapDescription" id="mapDescription">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="indent">
            <p>
                If you'd like to merge maps into an existing one of your own then select it from the list.<br>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="indent options">
            <h3>Your Current Perspectives</h3>

            <div id="mapList" class="container-fluid options">
                <div class="row columnTitle">
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <p>Map</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <p>Select</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p>
                Once you have made your selection, click Next.
            </p>
            <button id="nextMerge" type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Next</button>
        </div>

        <form method="get" action="/showGraphs">
            <div class="form-group indent">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">All Views</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div id="introNext" class="indent noDisplay">
        <p>
            You can merge up to five maps at a time into your new map. If you want to merge more then simply repeat the process and
            combine maps into previously merged ones.
        </p>
        <p>
            Enter the names of the maps that you would like to merge, as soon as you start typing you will see a list of maps that match your criteria.
        </p>
        <form class="form-horizontal" ref='mergeForm' id="mergeForm" method="post" action="/processMergeMaps" enctype="multipart/form-data" autocomplete="off">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="mapName1" class="col-md-1 control-label">Map 1</label>
                <div class="col-md-5">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control maps" name="mapName1" id="mapName1">
                    <input type="text" class="noDisplay" name="mapID1" id="mapID1">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="mapName2" class="col-md-1 control-label">Map 2</label>
                <div class="col-md-5">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control maps" name="mapName2" id="mapName2">
                    <input type="text" class="noDisplay" name="mapID2" id="mapID2">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="mapName3" class="col-md-1 control-label">Map 3</label>
                <div class="col-md-5">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control maps" name="mapName3" id="mapName3">
                    <input type="text" class="noDisplay" name="mapID3" id="mapID3">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="mapName4" class="col-md-1 control-label">Map 4</label>
                <div class="col-md-5">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control maps" name="mapName4" id="mapName4">
                    <input type="text" class="noDisplay" name="mapID4" id="mapID4">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="mapName5" class="col-md-1 control-label">Map 5</label>
                <div class="col-md-5">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control maps" name="mapName5" id="mapName5">
                    <input type="text" class="noDisplay" name="mapID5" id="mapID5">
                </div>
            </div>
            <input type="text" class="noDisplay" name="mapNameDest" id="mapNameDest">
            <input type="text" class="noDisplay" name="mapIDDest" id="mapIDDest">
            <button type="submit" class="col-md-offset-1 btn btn-primary">Merge</button>
        </form>

        <div class="indent options">
            <button id="mergeBack" type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Back</button>
            <form method="get" action="/showGraphs">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">All Views</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>
